*SELECT BUYER_GUID, GROSS_AMOUNT, ROUND( GROSS_AMOUNT, 0 ) AS GROSS_AMOUNT_ROUND,
*
*CEIL( GROSS_AMOUNT ) AS ROUND_AMOUNT
*
*FROM SNWD_SO INTO TABLE @DATA(ITAB).
*
*loop at itab into data(Is_tab).
*
*WRITE: / Is_tab-buyer_guid, Is_tab-gross_amount, Is_tab-gross_amount_round, Is_tab-round_amount.
*
*ENDLOOP.

